- @page = { title: 'Projects', 'navbar-title': 'Projects' }
.container
  .row{ class: 'justify-content-center mt-2 mx-2'}
    .card-columns
      .card
        .card-body
          %h2{ class: 'card-title text-xs-center' } blog
          %p{ class: 'card-text text-muted' }
          %p.card-text The source code for this blog, released in hopes that it will be of use to someone, somewhere. Built with Ruby on Rails 5, Twitter Bootstrap 4 (alpha), and Postgres, already configured for deployment to Heroku.
          = link_to 'GitHub', 'https://github.com/d3d1rty/blog'
      .card
        .card-body
          %h2{ class: 'card-title text-xs-center' } vbot
          %p{ class: 'card-text text-muted' }
          %p.card-text vbot is an IRC bot library that aims to be make building and extending IRC bots more efficient.
          = link_to 'GitHub', 'https://github.com/d3d1rty/vbot'
          %br
          = link_to 'RubyGems', 'https://rubygems.org/gems/vbot'
      .card
        .card-body
          %h2{ class: 'card-title text-xs-center' } dgen
          %p{ class: 'card-text text-muted' }
          %p.card-text Using the diceware method to generate passwords results in stronger passwords that are more resistant to cracking. This project implements the diceware method to create passphrases that are strong and easy to remember.
          = link_to 'GitHub', 'https://github.com/d3d1rty/dgen'
          %br
          = link_to 'RubyGems', 'https://rubygems.org/gems/dgen'
      .card
        .card-body
          %h2{ class: 'card-title text-xs-center' } gbud
          %p{ class: 'card-text text-muted' }
          %p.card-text This project aims to make starting a new gem project simple by automating the creation of all required files and directories for you.
          = link_to 'GitHub', 'https://github.com/d3d1rty/gbud'
          %br
          = link_to 'RubyGems', 'https://rubygems.org/gems/gbud'
      .card
        .card-body
          %h2{ class: 'card-title text-xs-center' } fb-sleep
          %p{ class: 'card-text text-muted' }
          %p.card-text This script aggregates the number of posts per hour based on information collected from a FB user's page. This data can then be analyzed to determine a user's typical sleep times.
          = link_to 'GitHub', 'https://github.com/d3d1rty/fb-sleep'
      .card
        .card-body
          %h2{ class: 'card-title text-xs-center' } clippings2xml
          %p{ class: 'card-text text-muted' }
          %p.card-text This script extracts information from the My Clippings.txt file generated by highlights on the Amazon Kindle ereader device and creates an XML document.
          = link_to 'GitHub', 'https://github.com/d3d1rty/clippings2xml'
